GoldenEye::

"Sure thing." She held Tails up to her face like she was feeling the 
squirrel pelt against her face. She whispered,"Now Tails, I want you 
to jump and run up into the trees as soon as I go to hand you over, 
jump and run for it. I'll catch up with you later on."

She walked over and was about to hand over the squirrel.  She reached 
out her arms and held the animal.
